{"tid":2059244,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"李傲然：由於不會要求參選人簽署共同綱領，可能重新參選","createTime":"2020-06-10T18:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T09:07:47.000Z","uid":104767,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9f5a5c2404b0e08b4d73d9264995f13afe62e828","tid":2059244,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:41:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1887372994906575/posts/2516222852021583?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1887372994906575%2Fposts%2F2516222852021583%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRC9NcCfN%2BV0%2B2kMkFhSspzA%3D&h=eeb46c4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1887372994906575/posts/2516222852021583?sfns=mo</a><br />\n<br />\n當日本人李傲然退出九西初選，成全大局是為了35+而努力，同時亦完成了訂立「共同綱領」的任務。<br />\n<br />\n遺憾地原來最終卻「不會要求參選人簽署共同綱領」，此舉等同違背當日公開莊嚴的承諾，現時情況令香港人極度失望。<br />\n<br />\n若然當日的承諾只是信口開河，我當日頂住大批支持者的壓力，希望退出成全大局，最後卻換來更大的荒唐的話，我就不得不重新考慮，是否需要再度站出來為香港人繼續奮鬥。<br />\n<br />\n生而為人，要為香港人全力以赴，無負時代的呼喚。<br />\n<br />\n李傲然<br />\n10/06/2020"},{"pid":"e24c2dd814bdb41d83813a6690552148cf760129","tid":2059244,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"教協唔肯簽攬炒承諾書，似乎係破壞35+戰線嘅元兇。"},{"pid":"210345bd2828d7336414a21adab4cd16ec84e3c0","tid":2059244,"uid":265485,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e24c2dd814bdb41d83813a6690552148cf760129","tid":2059244,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:44:05.000Z","msg":"教協唔肯簽攬炒承諾書，似乎係破壞35+戰線嘅元兇。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-11T05:12:17.000Z","msg":"問原因唔簽"},{"pid":"fb9cfc622a7de8a330916fd7be4ffa994b8da5af","tid":2059244,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-13T09:07:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}